trans-unit.source: Provides utilities to support the exporting of COM+ SOAP-enabled application proxies by the server and the importing of the proxies by the client.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona utilidades que admiten que el servidor exporte servidores proxy de aplicación COM+ con SOAP habilitado y el cliente los importe.

trans-unit.source: The utility functions that <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ISoapUtility> provides are called from numerous locations within COM+; however, their primary purpose is to support the export and import of client proxies.
trans-unit.target: Funciones de la utilidad <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ISoapUtility> proporciona se llaman desde varias ubicaciones dentro de COM +; sin embargo, su objetivo principal es admitir la exportación e importación de servidores proxy de cliente.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.SoapUtility> for the default implementation.
trans-unit.target: Consulte <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.SoapUtility> para la implementación predeterminada.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ISoapUtility> is used internally by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ISoapUtility> se utiliza internamente por .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: You do not need to use it directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: No es necesario utilizar directamente en el código.
